            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic requiescit in <lb n="2"/>pace Leo qui fuit <lb n="3"/>conductor dom<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>ni</abbr></expan> <lb n="4"/>nostri an<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>us</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> XX et vix<lb break="no" n="5"/>it annus <note>sic</note> LXX et menses <lb n="6"/>VIII dies XX et sepultus <lb n="7"/>Maximo <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> cons<lb break="no" n="8"/>ule diae <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>Kalend</abbr><ex>arum</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/>Iuliarum indi<lb break="no" n="10"/>ctione prima
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Wiederverwendung der Stele als Stufe. Z. 7 ff.: flüchtiger eingemeißelt, nach Bestattung genaues Datum nachgetragen. Q ähnelt einem P. (B): ILCV 351, de Rossi: Z. 4/5: vix/it annus XXX; CIL XI 549: Z. 1: requeiscit.</p>
            </div>
